3rd party applications (netwrok virtual appliances) to analyze and inspect.
GWB spreads the traffic into NVA first and then either send or drop the traffic.
Operates at layer3(Network layer)- IP packets

two functions:
TRANSPARENT NETWORK GATEWAY
LOAD BALANCER

uses the GENEVE protocol on port 6081.

